modName: SkyTEST Realistic Animals and Predators fomod
summary: A fomod for those that like to see information on mods in NMM.
descriptionHtml:
This is a FOMOD addin for the main file SkyTEST Realistic animals n predators here at http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10175

If you already have it installed then UNINSTALL it but do NOT delete it. 

 Move it to the UNASSIGNED catagory.  Exit NMM.

Copy the FOMOD directory from this file into the main file.  A FOMOD directory should have been created by NMM but it\'ll have a blank file in it.  Just overwrite.

Start NMM again.  The FOMOD info will now be shown.
author: thorne67
